text: Simeon Šutev (born 21 November 1942) is a Yugoslav wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle 57 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:Living people Category:Yugoslav male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Yugoslavia Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Štip
